                    <span>This book was very disappointing. The author goes through endless verbose and meandering discussions of software engineering, but doesn't have a clue how to write decent code. The examples are pitiful--poorly designed, hard to follow, and sloppy.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An advert not a book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
